ign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> 8th Shawl - feedback</span><hr size=1> Feeding back my experience of the 8th shawl quest from last night (Gratz Cadira on the shawl!)<br>
<br>
The general starts from the beach close to the ice bridge. The only thing to remember here is to turn in the armour, wait for him to respawn, THEN hand him the orders. The second you hand the orders in he starts walking.<br>
<br>
He didn't seem to aggro roamers (although they aggro'd us just fine!). Two of the encounters are near square structures - the mobs just pop right next to them. Our two groups of 60's handled them without problem.<br>
<br>
Someone managed to target and hit the general. I tried to mezz then blur - the general CANNOT be mezzed, but can be blurred.<br>
<br>
We dealt with the final encounter, which is by a tree just before a small chain of ice islands. This is where it all went wrong. The general tried to walk across the islands, pathed into the water, then WARPED back to the start point.<br>
<br>
Once we'd established this, and that he was still wearing the armour (so the quest hadn't reset), we sent someone to aggro him and drag him back. There are two gnomes on the ice islands that he is supposed to talk with before continuing on to the gnome camp. We dragged him to those damn gnomes a dozen times and blurred him - every time he started heading back to his start point.<br>
<br>
Finally, we dragged him to the far side of the ice islands, closer to the gnome camp, and blurred him. Hey Presto, he starts walking to the gnome camp, makes his speech and the Avatar of below spawns.<br>
<br>
We also got a snowchipper, ice helmet and drakkel claws as bonus loot, so all in all not a bad evening.<br>
<br>
Cen. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=595.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=595.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=595.topic><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=595.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.threadControl?topicID=595.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=595.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=595.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm51">Manaburn Nerf Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilat